  "title": "Car Mechanic [South, Monthly Bonus]",
  "description": "<h3>Job Title: Car Mechanic</h3><p><strong>Working Days:</strong> 6 days per week<br /><strong>Working Hours: </strong>9AM-6PM<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> S$2500-3000 + OT + Monthly Bonus</p><h3>Job Responsibilities:</h3><ul><li><p>Perform vehicle servicing and routine maintenance</p></li><li><p>Diagnose and repair engine, brake, suspension, and electrical issues</p></li><li><p>Carry out inspection and troubleshooting of vehicles</p></li><li><p>Replace faulty parts and ensure repair quality</p></li><li><p>Keep tools and work area clean and safe</p></li><li><p>Follow workshop safety rules and procedures</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements:</h3><ul><li><p>Experience as a car / automotive mechanic</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of vehicle systems and diagnostics</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and in a team</p></li><li><p>Responsible and willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Relevant technical certificate is an advantage<br /></p><p>﻿Aurora AsiaPacific (21C0671) | Stephanie Luan (R21100585)</p></li></ul>",
